  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The creature inside wriggles and flexes its fluffy toes, yearning to feel soil between them.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">protective</span> disposition, brimming with affection for its Traveler companion.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个有生命的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">准备孵化！</span><br><br>里面的生物扭动着身子，蜷曲着毛茸茸的脚趾，渴望能感受到泥土的触感。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">保护他人</span>的基因潜质，对它的旅行者同伴满怀情谊。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個有生命的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且準備孵化！</span><br><br>這隻生物在裡面扭動身子，伸展著毛茸茸的腳趾，渴望感受腳趾間的泥土。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">具有保護欲</span>，對旅行者同伴充滿愛意。"
  },
